415
00:30:53,150 --> 00:30:54,320
Do you know the poet...

416
00:30:55,550 --> 00:30:56,790
Kim Pil Hyun?

417
00:31:00,790 --> 00:31:02,230
That's my great-grandmother.

418
00:31:03,060 --> 00:31:04,860
This was her when she was young.

419
00:31:07,470 --> 00:31:11,740
As a woman, she was an ordinary housewife.

420
00:31:12,940 --> 00:31:16,510
Then she became a man and wrote frantically.

421
00:31:18,680 --> 00:31:19,710
That...

422
00:31:20,810 --> 00:31:22,720
