821
00:56:04,300 --> 00:56:07,200
You'd better not show up in my neighbourhood again.

822
00:56:27,690 --> 00:56:29,690
Your name was Min Dong Gi, right?

823
00:56:30,020 --> 00:56:31,490
Who are you?

824
00:56:31,890 --> 00:56:34,360
Who am I? I'm the protector of justice.

825
00:56:35,960 --> 00:56:37,290
Are you Park Yoon Jae's girlfriend?

826
00:56:38,630 --> 00:56:39,830
You must know who I am.

827
00:56:40,330 --> 00:56:42,570
I'm telling you this because you know who I am.

828
00:56:42,770 --> 00:56:45,670
This better be the last time you mention Yoon Jae's name.

829
00:56:46,370 --> 00:56:48,140
Or I'm going to make you pay.

830
00:56:48,640 --> 00:56:49,810
I'll make you pay too.

831
00:56:51,340 --> 00:56:52,840
Beat it. Seriously.

832
00:56:53,080 --> 00:56:54,140
My gosh.

833
00:56:58,480 --> 00:56:59,520
Come inside now.

834
00:57:01,290 --> 00:57:02,750
Stay here for a bit and then go.

835
00:57:03,420 --> 00:57:05,860
It's not because I'm worried about you or being thoughtful.

836
00:57:06,590 --> 00:57:08,560
It's just that the guy you were dealing with is a total psycho.

837
00:57:09,890 --> 00:57:11,760
Well, if you want to go home, you can.

838
00:57:16,930 --> 00:57:18,500
I kept telling myself...

839
00:57:19,070 --> 00:57:21,410
that it couldn't be and it just wasn't possible.

840
00:57:22,970 --> 00:57:25,840
But only Ji Hoon and I know about what happened before.

841
00:57:29,050 --> 00:57:30,680
How did you know about Min Dong Gi?

842
00:57:40,620 --> 00:57:42,930
I took pity on you and helped you.

843
00:57:43,490 --> 00:57:44,660
You're talking nonsense.

844
00:57:45,300 --> 00:57:46,700
Hey, get out of my house.

845
00:57:49,630 --> 00:57:52,070
(Kim Ji Hoon)

846
00:58:08,850 --> 00:58:09,920
(Kang Min Joo)

847
00:58:09,990 --> 00:58:11,119
The person you have reached is unavailable.

848
00:58:11,120 --> 00:58:13,090
You'll be directed to voicemail.

849
00:58:13,360 --> 00:58:14,360
Please leave...

850
00:58:15,960 --> 00:58:17,360
(Kim Ji Hoon)

851
00:58:32,510 --> 00:58:33,809
The person you have reached is unavailable.

852
00:58:33,810 --> 00:58:35,710
You'll be directed to voicemail.

853
00:58:38,420 --> 00:58:39,920
(Kim Ji Hoon)

854
00:58:44,590 --> 00:58:46,590
The last 4 digits, 6734. It's you, isn't it?

855
00:58:48,360 --> 00:58:49,460
Kim Ji Hoon.

856
00:59:10,780 --> 00:59:12,020
The last 4 digits, 6734.

857
00:59:14,390 --> 00:59:16,890
Yes. It's me.

858
00:59:19,760 --> 00:59:20,820
Kim Ji Hoon.

859
00:59:21,290 --> 00:59:23,960
(Kang Min Joo)

860
00:59:38,910 --> 00:59:42,480
(Special thanks to Yoon Joo Sang and Park Myung Shin)

861
01:00:11,910 --> 01:00:15,480
(My Girlfriend is the Man!)

862
01:00:16,210 --> 01:00:17,780
Did I change back again?

863
01:00:18,480 --> 01:00:19,549
How much longer will you trouble Yoon Jae...

864
01:00:19,550 --> 01:00:21,520
just for your own happiness?

865
01:00:21,750 --> 01:00:24,220
Please don't tell the others about this.

866
01:00:24,890 --> 01:00:27,620
Are you two really in a romantic relationship?

867
01:00:27,690 --> 01:00:30,090
We must have thought lightly of this whole thing.

868
01:00:30,360 --> 01:00:31,630
I have a favour to ask you.

869
01:00:32,030 --> 01:00:33,230
Please break up with me.

870
01:00:33,830 --> 01:00:35,100
I need to drink today.

871
01:00:35,370 --> 01:00:37,230
Ji Eun!

872
01:00:38,400 --> 01:00:40,870
Right. It's over...

873
01:00:41,570 --> 01:00:43,210
between us.
